Now you have nothing to think.
Follow your selfish desires.
Follow your natural instinct.
After all you're just an animal.
It's much easier than trying to think.`</field></block></value><next><block type="array_insertAt" id="3Yj{q/)JIFd=.%`p1aaI"><value name="list"><block type="variables_get" id="/hF|r-j-#Ag?vGcom}qz"><field name="VAR" id="o/Sm,,BA$/I:7Gqb$umW">death_quotes</field></block></value><value name="index"><block type="lists_length" id="d)Rp]p!ueVmZUlE?8ZZy"><value name="VALUE"><block type="variables_get" id="/oBBZ]C~JBoaP,iK3G=#"><field name="VAR" id="o/Sm,,BA$/I:7Gqb$umW">death_quotes</field></block></value></block></value><value name="value"><block type="typescript_expression" id="qt385~l_+`b:9WVN1b=a"><field name="EXPRESSION">`With every bite with bone and skin.
The temple groaned and shook again.
His dwelling place did I neglect.
